OL,3,CCountdown under way for first manned
OL,4,CMoon mission in more than 50 years
OL,6,FNasa's first manned mission to the
OL,7,FMoon in more than 50 years that will
OL,8,Ftake its crew deeper into space than
OL,9,Fanyone has gone before is "ready to
OL,10,Fgo", according to space agency chiefs.
OL,12,FFour astronauts ` three US and one
OL,13,FCanadian ` are due to blast off aboard
OL,14,Fthe 322-foot rocket from Cape
OL,15,FCanaveral in Florida on Wednesday, if
OL,16,Fweather conditions hold and barring
OL,17,Fany last-minute hitches.
OL,19,FThe 10-day test flight will see the
OL,20,Fteam fly around the Moon and back on a
OL,21,Fmammoth 685,000-mile journey.
OL,26,@qD@[OUrD@CO]
