OL,3,CCountdown under way for first manned
OL,4,CMoon mission in more than 50 years
OL,6,FDuring the so-called lunar flyby, the
OL,7,FOrion spacecraft will travel around
OL,8,F4,700 miles beyond the far side of
OL,9,FEarth's natural satellite, setting a
OL,10,Fnew record.
OL,12,FWhile the astronauts will not
OL,13,Ftouchdown on the Moon, the Artemis II
OL,14,Fmission paves the way for a future
OL,15,Flunar landing within the next couple
OL,16,Fof years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
