FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774933458
OL,3,CCountdown under way for first manned
OL,4,CMoon mission in more than 50 years
OL,6,FThe UK is playing a part in the
OL,7,Fmission, with the Goonhilly Earth
OL,8,FStation, near Helston, Cornwall,
OL,9,Fhelping to track the capsule on its
OL,10,Fepic celestial voyage.
OL,12,FSpeaking at a news conference at
OL,13,FFlorida's Kennedy Space Centre, Nasa
OL,14,Fassociate administrator Amit Kshatriya
OL,15,Fsaid: "As we enter the pre-launch
OL,16,Fphase, the teams are in a strong
OL,17,Fposture, and the mission remains on
OL,18,Ftrack."
OL,20,FHe added: "The vehicle is ready. The
OL,21,Fsystem is ready. The crew is ready."
OL,26,@wD@GOUzD@GO]|D@KOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
