PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774933458
OL,3,CCountdown under way for first manned
OL,4,CMoon mission in more than 50 years
OL,6,FHe went on: "I have complete
OL,7,Fconfidence in this team of the Nasa
OL,8,Fworkforce. For everybody else, 53
OL,9,Fyears ago humanity left the Moon and
OL,10,Fdid not return. Now we go back."
OL,12,FArtemis launch director Charlie
OL,13,FBlackwell-Thompson said the countdown
OL,14,Fto launch started at 4.44pm local time
OL,15,Fon Monday.
OL,17,FShe added: "It is an exciting time.
OL,18,FIt's an exciting time for this team
OL,19,Fand our crew and really our nation and
OL,20,Fthe world.
OL,26,@nD@MOUrD@`O]yD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
