PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774933458
OL,3,CCountdown under way for first manned
OL,4,CMoon mission in more than 50 years
OL,6,F"All indications are right now we're
OL,7,Fin excellent, excellent shape as we
OL,8,Fget into count."
OL,10,FNasa chief flight director Emily
OL,11,FNelson said: "Our teams in mission
OL,12,Fcontrol and our crew members have been
OL,13,Fspent the last two years dedicated to
OL,14,Ftraining for this particular mission,
OL,15,Fdeveloping all of the products
OL,16,Fassociated with this flight, and they
OL,17,Fare ready to go.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@PO]sD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
