OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774933458
OL,3,CCountdown under way for first manned
OL,4,CMoon mission in more than 50 years
OL,6,F"The opportunity is immense for us to
OL,7,Ffinally get the opportunity to send
OL,8,Four crew farther than anyone's gone
OL,9,Fbefore."
OL,11,FThe mission previously had to be
OL,12,Fpostponed by two months due to
OL,13,Fhydrogen fuel leaks and clogged helium
OL,14,Flines.
OL,16,FThe last time Nasa sent astronauts to
OL,17,Fthe Moon was during Apollo 17 in 1972.
OL,19,FThe new Artemis programme aims for a
OL,20,Ftwo-person landing in 2028.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@HO]
